HOW IT WORKED FOR ME:
1.) If you have WINRAR installed, just use it to unrar (just search piratebay for it + key). Select the first file and extract. WINRAR will handle the rest.
2.) If you have a virtual drive program installed like MAGIC ISO or POWER ISO you can use it to mount the ISO file.
3.) And then, wolla!!!
